    "title": "Return Visit",
    "language": "en",
    "originalLanguage": "en",
    "text": "This was our second visit this year, as soon as we stepped in the door we were greeted with warmth and kindness, Maggie had taken our booking a while ago and had truly fulfilled our requests, it was so good to meet her. Once again the Breakfast is amazing, such an huge selection. We never tire of the wonderful view from the 14th floor. Every single person that works there in any area offer the highest customer service, they make you feel very special, and absolutely nothing is too much trouble. We will never stay anywhere else than the Royal Lancaster when visiting London. \nThank you for everything.",
