    "title": "Excellent stay - highly recommend ",
    "language": "en",
    "originalLanguage": "en",
    "text": "We have just returned from a fully 5* experience at the Royal Lancaster Hotel. From the friendly welcome of door and reception staff when we arrived, we knew we were on to a good thing. Our room had the most incredible view over London, from where we identified many key landmarks. The room itself, like the hotel, was designed with elegance and functionality. The bed was super comfortable.\nAnother of our highlights was the inspired range of food available at breakfast - something for everyone.\nThank you to all the staff at the hotel for making our stay so memorable for all the right reasons!",
