    "originalLanguage": "en",
    "text": "We returned to the Royal Lancaster, and the experience was just as excellent as always. The hospitality and politeness of the staff were impeccable, nothing to complain about. I met Maggie again after some time since our last visit. She took care of us and arranged a room with a lovely view as a gesture for our loyalty. Matt at the concierge was also very helpful with his bar recommendations. This time we didn’t have enough time for dining, but maybe next time.\n\nThank you for everything. We look forward to seeing visit again next time.",
