    "originalLanguage": "en",
    "text": "Went to the Hyde Cafe yesterday with one of my best friends for the Halloween themed Afternoon Tea and we were both incredibly impressed with the quality of the food and, even more so, by the amazing staff! We felt looked after and cared for during our entire time there. \nAll the little personal touches were really appreciated and I wanted to shout out the wonderful Hafize, Daniela, Iolanda, Asia and Trina who made our afternoon so special.\n\nHighly recommended :D!!",
