    "title": "A nice touch of luxury",
    "language": "en",
    "originalLanguage": "en",
    "text": "What a beautiful hotel. Clean and very comfortable and a short walk to Hyde Park. After a long flight from Sydney I arrived at the hotel around 7.30am and  thinking that I wouldn’t be able to check in that early I was pleasantly surprised when they said my room was ready….And what a lovely room it was. Great shower and toiletries. A desk and a lounge sofa made this a very pleasant stay ( 3 nights) ..  Everything you would want or need.. \nA very inviting coffee lounge ,2  restaurants and a terrific bar... Breakfast was Continental or cooked with loads of choice. Very attentive staff and great doorman to help you with your luggage or get you a Taxi.. \nHope to stay there again one day…..",
