    "title": "Wonderful stay at the Royal Lancaster",
    "language": "en",
    "originalLanguage": "en",
    "text": "Great hotel, great location, great team (super friendly, listens and delivers) and great design, especially the rooms. The only improvement request would be to upgrade the beds - it looks great and is fitted with wonderful sheets but do not have a comfortable pillow top which is essential in a quality, modern hotel.",
