    "title": "My favourite Hotel in London !",
    "language": "en",
    "originalLanguage": "en",
    "text": "I have used the Royal Lancaster for some 30 years.  It is ideally located for good and easy access to Heathrow Airport and London City.  The Hotel is stunning after a fairly recent total refurb.  Staff are friendly and very attentive and match the huge investment made in the Hotel.",
