    "text": "Well what can I say other than the biggest thank you for such a lovely stay! we booked our 2 night stay for our wedding anniversary and the staff went absolutely beyond our expectations, our room overlooked the Italian gardens just stunning, from the balloons, towel swans and romantic macaroons in our room, gorgeous bed linens and flurry pillows, the exceptional staff at breakfast, everything was just perfect.\nHonestly we had the best stay and cant wait to return.",
