    "originalLanguage": "en",
    "text": "What an absolutely fantastic experience! Every time we are back to the Royal Lancaster, we feel special from the moment we step in. Thanks again for such an unbelievable experience this weekend celebrating a birthday, we absolutely LOVED everything about our stay. We were speechless when we saw the room and we appreciated so much everything you did to make our stay beyond exceptional!\nA huge thank-you to all the amazing staff, everything was absolutely perfect. We can't wait to be there again!",
