      "text": "Dear DVicinanza,\n\nThank you ever so much for having taken the time to share this wonderful review following your recent stay with us. I am delighted to see that your expectations were exceeded on all fronts on this special occasion, and rest assured your kind comments have been shared and celebrated with the entire team. I hope to have the pleasure of welcoming you back again soon and should you ever require any assistance at all with the making of future reservations, I remain entirely at your disposal.\n\nKind Regards,\nAlexander Henskens\nHotel Manager\nAhenskens@royallancaster.com",
