    "originalLanguage": "en",
    "text": "The amazing royal Lancaster hotel \nWe had an unforgettable stay at this hotel for our weekend getaway! The atmosphere was romantic and peaceful, perfect for couples. The staff made us feel right at home two funny men’s the porterRyan and Vitality , and the room was beautifully decorated with stunning views. The location was ideal for exploring local attractions and enjoying quiet evenings. We highly recommend this hotel for couples looking for a relaxing and memorable experience!\" I want say big thanks to Doorman Amr for helping us a lot",
