    "text": "Both our delightful festive tea menu and the care given by our servers were excellent.  Tiana, Jules, & Damela took extra care to ensure that we understood the multiple tea and food menu options and delivered them beautifully. They took time to answer our questions about the hotel in general and the delightful decor in particular. Bravo to the owners for hiring such a wonderful staff and for delivering such a superior experience. Our Christmas is brighter thanks to this very memorable holiday experience at the Royal Lancaster❣️",
