    "title": "Great stay",
    "language": "en",
    "originalLanguage": "en",
    "text": "The actual Royal Lancaster hotel is beautiful. Perfect location walking distance to Hyde park and winter wonderland and more like Oxford Street  Westfield, soho and manything \nroom cleaning everyday  they were never filled and had to call the front desk a couple of times. The day shift front desk Dan, was very friendly and amazing , the food was delicious and Mohamed he is fantastic gentleman \n\nThe Doorman Amr at the front door was exceptional!!! Always smiling always helpful and just a truly nice man we spent a few times just chatting with him, and loved his accent!!! Thank you Amr for all that you do , another one luggage porter call Jaimie he is hardworking Man he look after our luggage very well and offer us transportation \nthanks  again to everyone gave us a good service at royal Lancaster hotel it’s really five star hotel",
