    "title": "Comfortable, great staff and wonderful location.",
    "language": "en",
    "originalLanguage": "en",
    "text": "Visited for 4 nights at Christmas time in a triple room on 6th floor. Location is excellent with sweeping entrance and uniformed doormen to give the 5 star feel. Very comfortable room, great bed and no noise at night. Our first hotel experience with our 3 month old baby and the staff could not have been kinder or more helpful to us and our baby girl. Nertila even went to the length of washing our baby bottles every morning for us - this made our lives so much easier and I can’t thank her enough. Excellent food at breakfast and from the in room dining (Club sandwich was the best I’ve had anywhere). Miriam at breakfast was full of joy every morning and clearly genuinely loves the work does. Literally can’t think of a negative so I’ll leave it there! Thank you to everyone who worked so hard to make our stay so special.",
    "username": "downsouth123",
