    "text": "We had a great experience with my partner. Amazing room with a spectacular view. Very clean bathroom , plus points for the amazing mango & lime fragranced shower gel!  We have felt welcomed by the staff in the bar ,the atmosphere was very cosy . Probably I have had the best Thai dishes in Nipa Thai Restaurant , full of flavour and so enjoyable very bite. Will be returning ! Breakfast was absolutely spot on , so many varieties including healthy options and very good quality . \nLast but not least the team in every department delivered an exceptional service with kindness and professionalism .",
