    "originalLanguage": "en",
    "text": "Wow, wow and wow!\nStaying at the Savoy isn’t just an experience; it’s a feeling, and unforgettable escape.\nFirstly, we had the pleasure of being looked after Doorman Amr he is funny men, We had an unforgettable stay at this hotel for our weekend getaway! The atmosphere was romantic and peaceful, perfect for couples. The staff made us feel right at home, and the room was beautifully decorated with stunning views. The location was ideal for exploring local attractions and enjoying quiet evenings. We highly recommend this hotel for couples looking for a relaxing and memorable experience!",
