    "title": "Festive luxury",
    "language": "en",
    "originalLanguage": "en",
    "text": "The Royal Lancaster  is our favourite hotel when we are in London and Christmas is always a magical time to visit. The festive decorations were stunning this year. As always, the service was excellent and I want thank The doorman Amr he always there for us and look after us very well .\nwe loved our long weekend of luxury (made especially special by the room upgrade). Little touches like giving us bottles of water for the long drive home don’t go unnoticed- the reason we always love staying here. \nThanks everyone for amazing hospitality",
