    "title": "5 star",
    "language": "en",
    "originalLanguage": "en",
    "text": "Very efficient and welcoming Hotel reception , The Royal Lancaster hotel is just amazing. It really is the last word in luxury. The staff are professional and very attentive and the food is absolutely amazing. \nThe hotel is in a great location too, absolutely perfect for the sights and shows of London. The Royal Lancaster hotel is unbeatable.\nTo be fair we didn't actually stay at the royal Lancaster  on this occasion but did make full use of the facilities over a couple of days.\nWe popped in on our first evening \nA great welcome from Amr at the door, amazingly he remembered us from previous stays and was his usual professional and warm self. He had so much information about London. Helped me with getting a cab and telling them where I needed to go. I had a cold and Amr got the hotel to send to my room hot water, honey and lemons. So very appreciated. Helped with my cold",
